Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.54,0:01:02.33,OPEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Fly high，make it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.52,0:01:05.74,OPEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Get to the new world that I seek
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.08,0:01:11.97,OPEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Someday，with my little wings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.55,0:01:18.45,OPEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Don't look back to the sorrow I left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.81,0:01:24.58,OPEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Here's my real intention I hide
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.27,0:01:31.33,OPEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I wish you were here，and so just right by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.67,0:01:37.74,OPEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Need to be strong enough to swallow my pride
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.10,0:01:43.59,OPEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I have been looking for my own style
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.88,0:01:51.18,OPEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Don't give it up，here comes the life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.05,0:01:56.66,OPEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Be alive，take it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.94,0:02:00.08,OPEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Promise to find，yes I will
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.41,0:02:06.45,OPEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Shining wings filled with wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.83,0:02:09.52,OPEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Fly high，make it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.64,0:02:12.87,OPEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Get to the new world that I seek
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.19,0:02:19.46,OPEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Someday，so I believe
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.15,0:23:49.77,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}変わらない毎日めぐりめぐる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.84,0:23:58.34,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}何も無い時間が過ぎる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.38,0:24:08.75,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}風にゆらめいて歩き出せば
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.00,0:24:19.31,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いつか変わるかな？　明日
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.35,0:24:31.73,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}無くしたものを　探しては　あきらめて
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.04,0:24:43.88,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一人佇み　空を見ていた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.15,0:23:49.77,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}重複著一成不變的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.84,0:23:58.34,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}空虛的時間從身旁流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.38,0:24:08.75,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}如果在風中邁出步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.00,0:24:19.31,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明天何時會改變
